article:
This is a list of properties and districts in Mississippi that are listed on the
National Register of Historic Places. There are 1,346 sites distributed among
all of Mississippi's 82 counties.

The locations of National Register properties and districts (at least for all
showing latitude and longitude coordinates below), may be seen in a Google map
by clicking on "Map of all coordinates".
